Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:05.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Largo Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:11.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Scattered throughout its beautiful waters\Nare throngs of islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,most of which being unexplored,\Nshrouding the Sea in a veil of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But admist those isles lies bountiful paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:27.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,teeming with undiscovered\Nflora, fauna, and mineral deposits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There, the shipwrecks of old are reclaimed by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And right now, I'm enjoying\Na little vacation here in those tropics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If only that were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get ready, whacky Demon Army racers!\NTime to find out who's the fastest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Luptă-te cu toată ființa ta ca să supraviețuiești
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:14.88,Song,,0,0,0,,și urmează raza de lumină către viitor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:28.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Trădat și abandonat în această lume pustie,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:34.29,Song,,0,0,0,,mă tem de ziua de mâine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:37.42,Song,,0,0,0,,și încerc să găsesc un loc pe care să-l pot numi „acasă”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:43.92,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart screams out, "I want to be needed"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:52.71,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to puzzle out these entwined identities, but can I trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Luptă-te ca să supraviețuiești
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:02:00.08,Song,,0,0,0,,și urmează raza de lumină către viitor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:03.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Chiar dacă vei pierde tot ceea ce ai obținut cu greu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:07.92,Song,,0,0,0,,nu-ți pierde și speranța
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Nu știu de ce sunt aici,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.50,Song,,0,0,0,,dar sunt în regulă cu acest lucru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:19.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Deoarece trebuie să merg mai departe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:25.29,Song,,0,0,0,,ca să pot zâmbi din nou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:41.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily is headed to Largo tomorrow on a logistics mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo? Why's she going that far out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon Army and the people of Largo\Nhave a steadfast, unbreakable alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:54.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo, huh... Land of the Dragonfolk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:59.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,About 3,000 years ago, Demon King Belial\Nled an attack on the human realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:10.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After his defeat, many denizens of\Nthe Demon World found peace with humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and became a diverse part of their society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dragonfolk attempted to do the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but when humans began to aggressively persecute them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it was clear coexistence was not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So they went off to live in peace in the Largo Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:39.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's correct, and the dragonfolk still\Nremember that painful history, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This was why they welcomed Queen Echidna's\Ninvasion with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's because of their stalwart support\Nand fervent assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that the Demon Army was able to continue\Nthe fight against humanity for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo is our army's lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:04.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dragonfolk, damn... Not surprised\Nthey're still holding that grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right. So you want me to head to Largo and\Nhelp out with the logistics mission, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The castle's food and equipment stores are running low,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so we need to make sure this shipment comes in safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that could be a serious issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's not the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's the mission plan Lily submitted to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gonna have a big happy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, this is how ALL of her reports look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Despite being entrusted with enough\Nmanpower to carry out her mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it takes longer than usual for her to complete it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:44.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So why're you sending me? Why not send Edvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's dragonfolk himself, and from Largo.\NHe's gotta know stuff that can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't send him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We need him to protect the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll get that. And I'll get that one, too!\NAnd the next one after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Plus, he'd end up doing everything himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily won't learn anything if he does all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you want me to go and keep an eye on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:13.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here I joined the Demon Army\Nto be stuck on babysitting duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If that's my job, I'll do it.\NI want to get hired on permanently, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can use a warp portal to get to Largo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't go missing me too much now, mmkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:33.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please make preparations to leave as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are we SURE she's a succubus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm finally here in Largo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Congrats on getting second place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:20.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Third and fourth did a real good job, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily, can we stop playing around now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were racing to see who could carry\Nthe supplies the fastest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Scuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got a whole lot more to transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've only done one trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's enough for today! Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, take this, it'll make you feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Down we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Say 'ahh'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no way we're finishing at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo has a warp portal between Largo\Nand the Demon Queen's palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and the isle's storage and logistics facilities\Nare brimming with supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If the individual strengths of the isle's myriad\Nraces were used effectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,with the right person assigned for every job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:29.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it would take a day, two days at the longest,\Nto get this job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If the right person were assigned\Nto the right  job, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo, take one! It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go pass them out to everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, have some carrots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So... Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, let me introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's really cool, this is my future husband, L--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:01.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Black Knight Onyx! And we are NOT betrothed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone's invited to our wedd--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're not having a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, fine! Force my hand, why don't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I need you to focus on these repairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? The heck are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:26.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? Any change in procedure\Nhas to be signed off on by the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:43.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dammit. I'm just a temp!\NI can't do anything 'round here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the isle's inhabitants have lodged\Ndozens of complaints against us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't apologize more for what we've done,\Nbut I hope this helps a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, the resupply\Nwill be the least of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll end up losing the dragonfolk and the logistics\Ncenter altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if that happens, then it's only a matter of time\Nbefore the Demon Army goes under!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why the long face, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sick? Wanna eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wanna lay down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, metaphorically, not literally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You need medicine! Does anyone have medicine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's such a sweet kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.96,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Does anyone around here have medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.25,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have the supplies from Largo arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not yet, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Think the job's too big for the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:46.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily is one of the Four Generals, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our forces, wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Half of our castle's facilities in ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:59.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, but thankfully, there wasn't a single casualty\Nin the battle against the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which means he was going easy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We threw everything we had at him in that battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:13.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but it might as well have been nothing to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Demon Queen is an embarrassment to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:25.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I found this growing by the gate! It's a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:31.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! Let's plant a ton of flowers in the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'd look sooo pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right. Thank you, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lily understands what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I seriously hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll trade you this carrot for some medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Someone, please, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:09.71,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,I need some medicine for someone whose head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sadly, she's still too immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't get through to her with logic like I would Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.54,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Leo's feeling really sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad she's so worried about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:20.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I wish she'd spend half that energy--hell,\Na tenth of that energy working instead of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:31.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got you some medicine for your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Does your head hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got bit by a snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:39.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a death viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You guessed it: I summoned this venomous viper,\Nand it's gonna help Lily mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, Leo, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the end of the line for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As powerful as I am, I'll be dead twelve hours from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know, Shutina can heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The warp portal's busted. We can't get back to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I made sure that nobody in the isles of Largo\Nhad the skill to be able to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which means there's only one other way to save my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go and pick some medicine herbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just like I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:19.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Some should be growing up on the western peaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, my vision's growing dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is west to the right or the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The western peaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cleanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And all the trials I've prepped on the road\Nto the western peaks are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:06.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To get through them, she'll need to manage\Nher people right and use the power of teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, these trials were designed\Nto teach her how to manage a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:14.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the pinnacle of on-the-job training!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Herbs on the western peaks!\NHerbs on the western peaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:22.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Herbs on the western peaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's finally transformed into Fenrir, the Divine Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Divine Wolf is a protective deity\Non the continent of Erkia, Lily's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have no idea why she's able to transform\Ninto something that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can anyone in her tribe do that, or is she just special?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing I know for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's already reached the first trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've cast an invincibility spell on this huge boulder\Nto nullify physical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this rock the kind you can't break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To break through, she'll need to find\Na subordinate who can remove the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't break it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Grr! I'm in a hurry, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:44.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She'll figure it out soon: if she can't do something\Nherself, she can do it with a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And when she realizes that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:48.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Little more! Little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Little more! Little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A little more? Don't be stupid!\NYou're not supposed to force your way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just give up and go to the nearest village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:06.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A whole troop of spellcasters is stationed there!\NYou can run there in less than a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She broke it. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She did it by herself, without\Nany help from her underlings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:36.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay! She can't get through the second trial herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This time, it'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Behold, infinitely replicating slimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are there more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eww!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Amongst all those slimes is a single,\Ntiny slime: the core slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take that one out, and the rest go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:11.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The fastest way to get through the trial\Nis to bring over a perceptive underling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She could even find someone who can cast ice magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A few more seconds, and you would\Nhave been at the bottom of that cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is my third trial, a crevasse\NI'd conjured up with gnomish power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If she wants to get to the western peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,she'll need to find a way to get to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who're you, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:19.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, my apologies. I am Godhart, a simple traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit back and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've concealed my smell, so she shouldn't know it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even with Lily's impressive leaping ability,\Nshe can't make that jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's only one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, how tragic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If only I had a friend who could fly!\NThey could help me fly across the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A friend... Could help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:06.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, when you can't solve a problem yourself,\Nyou can solve it with the help of a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:12.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow... Wow, yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mister God! I'm gonna go ask everyone for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Phew, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Had to get heavy-handed there,\Nbut now she'll realize the importance of teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now she just needs to put it into practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure she gets all the practice she needs,\Nand cover for any mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:38.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it that she grows into a fine leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mister God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:48.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I asked everyone for help, and they said\NI can just swim across the bottom then climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look! Your advice helped me get\Nto the other side! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Another failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Another failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Another failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Another failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you get the herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep! You feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. Real better. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... Ignorance truly is bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I wanna show you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, you drew me a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you think we could work like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you think this up all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nope. Mister God-- uh, Godheart, came up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He said it's way easier to work together\Nas a team than do something by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought a lot about it while you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:31.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm real stupid, so I won't figure\Nstuff out unless someone tells me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:37.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I assumed you could tell her something\Na hundred times and she wouldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought the only way to get through to her\Nwas by forcing her into the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, so, you think this'll make our work easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But in the end, I was the idiot, not Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe it won't work after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was tell her "hey, maybe try this".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this'll make it way easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good job, Lily! Superb work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone was super happy to split up\Nthe work and get it done faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I realized just how important it is to work as a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our Beast General is on her way to\Nbecoming quite the reliable leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess, though I could've done without\Nthe whole mock wedding ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing? It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, what do you need me for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. We've no time for small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, I have an important missive for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:53.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, I'm being made a permanent employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:22:00.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It comes straight from Queen Echidna:\N"Black Knight Onyx is to report to me at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? Crap, did she catch on to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:23.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Our hearts are always so frail and fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:30.13,Song,,0,0,0,,But we still face forward and continue down our long road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:35.79,Song,,0,0,0,,If we don't know something now, we can go learn about it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:42.71,Song,,0,0,0,,We might not know what's at the end of our long, continuing journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:48.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do everything yourself, lean on us sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:52.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Sharing your weaknesses is strength in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.92,Song,,0,0,0,,There' still a long way to go, so make sure you won't regret anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:00.33,Song,,0,0,0,,Dash on! The reason's simple
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:03.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Let loose! Make your dreams reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:09.92,Song,,0,0,0,,The future you're heading towards is one you shape yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:15.58,Song,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be scared of change, you can go little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.79,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to protect the things I cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.38,Song,,0,0,0,,(I'm so glad we found each other)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:26.71,Song,,0,0,0,,So I hope you hear how thankful I am for you
